<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,961,1004,1029]" pageId="31" pageNumber="221">
Identification key to the genera of adult 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Mulsant" authorityYear="1842" box="[650,745,1004,1029]" family="Scarabaeidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="31" pageNumber="221" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Oryctini">Oryctini</taxonomicName>
